name: Loli-Pop
description: The title name comes from words Lolita and Pop Art. 'Lolita' refers to young girls, while 'Pop Art' refers to drawing characteristic of Doodle Attack. The idea comes from combining RaptorVz's drawing style which is an anime style with Doodle Attack’s pop art style. And the fact they have something in common interests, they like music and Japanese culture.
